{"tid":2455820,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[字海] 毒撚反支那 就應該撐馬娘","createTime":"2021-03-21T11:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:29:34.000Z","uid":8307,"like":47,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7273d3f6a3b2e59ad367bf279b1d870557b13c","tid":2455820,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7CPxTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7CPxTL.jpg&h=b5378b60&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我地毒撚ACG界,<br />\n比支那入侵得愈黎愈嚴重<br />\n<br />\n原神幾受歡迎,就算唔肯面對<br />\n事實都擺在眼前<br />\n原神twitter又排第一,課金榜又霸左好耐第一<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有跟開都應該會知道<br />\n以前旗下既一隻驚shadowverse<br />\n曾經為左出支那版,而簽約將香港用戶既AC轉移去支那版<br />\n雖然最後冇轉到,不過都有出賣港人既意圖<br />\n但係cygames都仲係一間日資公司<br />\n旗下又有搞埋動畫公司,動畫串流平台之類<br />\n<br />\n最近cygames出左隻新驚馬娘<br />\n<img src=\"https://livedoor.blogimg.jp/jin115/imgs/f/9/f9c0c2ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fjin115%2Fimgs%2Ff%2F9%2Ff9c0c2ad.jpg&h=b87a771f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出左一個月到係日本既課金量<br />\n已經超越左日本原神今年頭三個月加埋既銷量<br />\n係twitter既討論到都非常之高<br />\n極之有期望砌低到原神<br />\n比日本仔上位都好過比支那仔上位<br />\n係咪先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWzeJ2J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWzeJ2J.gif&h=87bb9811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48084b0295d1da30eb5328474f55dea323d944db","tid":2455820,"uid":146340,"like":3,"dislike":43,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"我兩隻都玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0b4373fd0354f97f3cf78d2044c08d371efc22","tid":2455820,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"我哋唔係要馬娘贏，係要原神輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f0bb92eb24038d9ad845360d0e36f3edbf3489","tid":2455820,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor